# Copy this file to `jarvis_keys.txt` and put your real Google Gemini API keys below,
# one per line. Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Get free keys at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey  (one per Google account).
# The app rotates through them when one hits its daily free-tier limit.
#
# Alternatively, set the JARVIS_GEMINI_KEYS env var (comma-separated) instead of
# using this file — the env var takes priority.

YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_1_HERE
YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_2_HERE
